        <summary><span class="p2">Information<span></summary>
        <p>1. Eligibility:</p> 
        <p>   Anyone who is in need of a large meal!</p>
        <p>2. How to obtain the shared meal:</p>
        <p>   Fill in the form on the right and we will get back to you shortly!</p>
    </details>


    <br>

    <h2>Small Bites </h2>
    <img src ="smallbites.avif" alt="smallbites" width="500" height="300">
    <p>Small Bites lets peopel enjoy lighter, yet satisfying meals from restaurants that have extra small portions or snacks at the end of the day. These may include appetizers, sandwiches, salads, desserts, or other quick bites. Whether you’re in need of a snack or a smaller meal, Small Bites provides an accessible way to enjoy quality food without the need for a full meal.</p>
