        <summary><span class="p2">Information<span></summary>
            <p>1. Eligibility:</p> 
            <p>   Anyone who is in need of a large meal!</p>
            <p>2. How to obtain the shared meal:</p>
            <p>   Fill in the form on the right and we will get back to you shortly!</p>
    </details>
</div>
<div class="food-form-body">
    <form class="food-form">
      <label for="userName"><h4>Your Name:</h4></label>
      <input type="text" id="userName" name="userName" required=""><br>

      <label for="email"><h4>Your Email:</h4></label>
      <input type="text" id="email" name="email" required=""><br>

      <label for="reason"><h4>Required information(e.g. Allergies, Delivery/Pick-up):</h4></label><br>
      <textarea id="reason" name="reason" rows="4" required=""></textarea><br>

      <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
  </div>


</div>
</body>
